name: Nature-Cyber Hybrid Avatar #65
description: Introducing a stunning fusion of nature and futuristic technology from the RPine DEX aggregator collection, this avatar radiates natural elegance. Its glowing, intricate circuitry pattern weaves with foliage and organic elements, creating a mesmerizing balance between the forest and the digital realm. A collectible masterpiece within the RPine ecosystem.
